stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE

    IDLE --> RUNNING : start()
    RUNNING --> PAUSED : pause()
    RUNNING --> IDLE : stop()
    PAUSED --> RUNNING : resume() / start()
    PAUSED --> IDLE : stop()
    RUNNING --> SUSPENDED : sync()
    SUSPENDED --> RUNNING : syncComplete()
    SUSPENDED --> IDLE : stop()
    RUNNING --> ERROR_RECOVERY : errorDetected()
    ERROR_RECOVERY --> IDLE : reset()

    note right of IDLE
        Each state owns its
        valid transitions.
        Invalid = IllegalStateException
    end note

    note right of ERROR_RECOVERY
        6 states × 6 operations
        = 36 conditional branches
        WITHOUT State Pattern
    end note
